# Files Gemini's read_file / glob / read_many_files tools must never surface.
#
# run-predict sets context.fileFiltering.respectGitIgnore=false so the agent can
# read the case snapshot provisioned into the gitignored data/*/*/record/ path.
# That also stops .gitignore from hiding the runner-local, secret-bearing files
# below — chiefly .gemini/settings.json, into which `fedcourts mcp-config` writes
# the literal CourtListener API token. respectGeminiIgnore stays on by default and
# is independent of respectGitIgnore, so this list re-establishes a filesystem-level
# guard beneath the prompt contract's no-literal-secrets rule.
#
# Do NOT add data/*/*/record/ here — the predictor is meant to read it.
/.gemini/
/.codex/
/mcp-servers.json
/.env
/.envrc
/.dvc/config.local
